snippet.title: Sailor Cats 2: Space Odyssey - Android Gameplay
snippet.description:
Sailor Cats 2: Space Odyssey embark on a new journey in SPACE!

Looks like building a cardboard rocket wasn’t such a good idea after all because it exploded! 

Now all your cats are missing in space and you’ll have to find them! But don’t worry because you’ll also find lots of new friends - and marvelous creatures - along the way.

Sailor Cats 2: Space Odyssey FEATURES  :

⭐ Click-and-collect game
⭐ Easy to play - tap at the right time to fish!
⭐ More than 100 skins and costumes to dress up your kitties.
⭐ Upgrade your spaceship while fishing metals, coins & stars!
⭐ A whole galaxy to discover full of planets, nebulae, mechas and aliens
⭐ Great for kids, moms, grannies, crazy cat ladies and cool dudes alike. The whole family can play and enjoy Sailor Cats 2!
❤️ Unique cute kawaii graphic style

--

No additional purchases are needed to finish the game.
Offline game: No internet connection needed.
#HINT: Find all the relics to unlock special skins *wink*wink*

--

⭐ This game is made by a small but passionate young team so we really appreciate your feedback ^-^ We really hope you enjoy our game! We certainly had a blast making it. Even if you didn’t, we’d love to hear from you. Email us at help@platonicgames.com

Ready for a relaxing space adventure? 🚀

Google Play download URL:
https://play.google.com/store/apps/details?id=com.platonicgames.sailorcats2

New Games Every Day(Just Good Games) :
https://maximumandroid.net/newest-app
